title: Developer Discords
content: A web App for viewing a list of official programming and developer discord servers allows to search alphabetically or by search
short: Web App for Viewing a list of official developer related discord Communities

title: InstaDog
content: Instagram Clone but for Dogs! Like your posts and share them with url. Instadog utlizes a random dog Api for Images and videos while text is randomly generated.

title: CS Resources
content: Contains direct comparisions of Frameworks and Providers to build your projects, A curated list of over 600 free Apis, Reccomended Developer Tools, Datasets of computer science topics, flashcards, Scientific Calculator, Dictionary and more!
short: Web App filled with Computer Science Resources for Students

title: Octo Stats
content: A web App for viewing Github profile and repository stats with Chart Visualizations. Sort throught Repos by stars, forks, and size. View Recent events and commits Utilizing github Rest API
short: Website to better visualize Github Stats
